{"tid":2284082,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"支付寶求打賞 天后淪為國際乞丐 酒井法子生活拮据 金主出天價拍全裸寫真","createTime":"2020-11-13T04:41:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T15:17:46.000Z","uid":32511,"like":39,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"9ce9553c09cc318565a5892f7efb5931ddd3a4e7","tid":2284082,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T04:41:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/nGQd3Ta.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FnGQd3Ta.jpg&h=ea57d86f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有「擋泥板女神」封號的日本女星酒井法子，曾是紅極一時的玉女明星，未料2009年驚爆<br />\n染毒後，重創形象和經營多年的演藝事業，如今聲勢已經大不如前，甚至仍遭當地電視台<br />\n封殺，如今傳出為了賺取生活費的她，似乎有意考慮拍攝全裸寫真集。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20201112001980-260404?chdtv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20201112001980-260404%3Fchdtv&d=28xXuG3%2BZgR4L17YEenOIq%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=7b9e4958\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20201112001980-260404?chdtv</a>"},{"pid":"c451afa58d63aa28e55665d7607a5e5a9e6c5cc0","tid":2284082,"uid":33359,"like":45,"dislike":3,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T04:48:46.000Z","msg":"拍av<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拍av<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d06d56c3a1e4fc474a7b4c4f78c88f9eab35e525","tid":2284082,"uid":60109,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T04:49:00.000Z","msg":"會買<br />\n幾殘都會課金支持<br />\n幾時有？"},{"pid":"45ffed3983865c7d53fc5329fb022ed14d66e0a2","tid":2284082,"uid":282438,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T04:49:24.000Z","msg":"SOD 50路 合約準備左好耐喇"},{"pid":"d8325e5fedc3c72fc367dcab9b4d3d79d4997120","tid":2284082,"uid":32511,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T04:53:24.000Z","msg":"蝴蝶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asset